            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EBabylon%20was%20destined%20to%20fall.%20Even%20though%20Babylon's%20final%20demise%20was%20years%20in%20the%20future%2C%20Jeremiah%20could%20see%20through%20his%20prophetic%20eye%20that%20the%20time%20for%20Babylon's%20fall%20had%20come%20(Jeremiah%2051%3A13).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGod%20had%20used%20Babylon%20to%20destroy%20Jerusalem%2C%20and%20for%20many%20years%20the%20Babylonians%20ruled%20over%20the%20Jews%20to%20the%20glory%20of%20their%20false%20god.%20Now%20the%20time%20had%20arrived%20for%20the%20Medes%20to%20be%20stirred%20up%20to%20attack%20the%20seemingly%20invincible%20city%20of%20Babylon.%20History%20records%20that%20the%20Medes%20diverted%20the%20Euphrates%20River%2C%20which%20ran%20through%20the%20city%20of%20Babylon%2C%20and%20were%20able%20to%20penetrate%20the%20massive%20city%20walls%20in%20one%20night.%20When%20God%20gets%20ready%20to%20judge%20a%20proud%20nation%2C%20the%20curtain%20of%20history%20has%20closed%20for%20them!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJohn%20the%20Revelator%20foretold%20the%20same%20collapse%20for%20the%20future%20economic%20empire%20called%20Babylon%3A%20%22How%20terrible%2C%20how%20terrible%20for%20Babylon%2C%20that%20great%20city!%20In%20one%20single%20moment%20God's%20judgment%20came%20on%20her%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E(Revelation%2018%3A10).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt%20doesn't%20matter%20how%20great%2C%20lofty%2C%20and%20mighty%20the%20world's%20empires%20are-they%20will%20all%20fall%20before%20Jehovah%20God.%20His%20awesome%20power%20is%20described%20this%20way%3A%20%22The%20Lord%20is%20king!%20Let%20the%20nations%20tremble!%20He%20sits%20on%20his%20throne%20between%20the%20cherubim.%20Let%20the%20whole%20earth%20quake!%22%20(Psalm%2099%3A1).%20We%2C%20too%2C%20should%20tremble%2C%20remembering%20what%20happened%20to%20the%20great%20Babylon.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
