            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EJeremiah%2051%3A1-53%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_51_1%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2251%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EJeremiah%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E51%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20stir%20up%20a%20destroyer%20against%20Babylon%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20people%20of%20Babylonia.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E51%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eof%20Leb-kamai%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20code%20name%20for%20Babylonia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_51_2%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2251%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EForeigners%20will%20come%20and%20winnow%20her%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eblowing%20her%20away%20as%20chaff.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20will%20come%20from%20every%20side%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eto%20rise%20against%20her%20in%20her%20day%20of%20trouble.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_51_3%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2251%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20let%20the%20archers%20put%20on%20their%20armor%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eor%20draw%20their%20bows.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20spare%20even%20her%20best%20soldiers!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3ELet%20her%20army%20be%20completely%20destroyed.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E51%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20Hebrew%20term%20used%20here%20refers%20to%20the%20complete%20consecration%20of%20things%20or%20people%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20either%20by%20destroying%20them%20or%20by%20giving%20them%20as%20an%20offering.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_51_4%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2251%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20will%20fall%20dead%20in%20the%20land%20of%20the%20Babylonians%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E51%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3EChaldeans%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2051%3A54.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eslashed%20to%20death%20in%20her%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_51_5%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2251%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehas%20not%20abandoned%20Israel%20and%20Judah.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EHe%20is%20still%20their%20God%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eeven%20though%20their%20land%20was%20filled%20with%20sin%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eagainst%20the%20Holy%20One%20of%20Israel.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_51_6%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2251%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EFlee%20from%20Babylon!%20Save%20yourselves!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20get%20trapped%20in%20her%20punishment!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EIt%20is%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20time%20for%20vengeance%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehe%20will%20repay%20her%20in%20full.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_51_7%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2251%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EBabylon%20has%20been%20a%20gold%20cup%20in%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20hands%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ea%20cup%20that%20made%20the%20whole%20earth%20drunk.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20nations%20drank%20Babylon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20wine%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20it%20drove%20them%20all%20mad.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_51_8%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2251%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20suddenly%20Babylon%2C%20too%2C%20has%20fallen.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EWeep%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EGive%20her%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EPerhaps%20she%20can%20yet%20be%20healed.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22jere_51_9%22%20bk%3D%22jere%22%20ch%3D%2251%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EWe%20would%20have%20helped%20her%20if%20we%20could%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebut%20nothing%20can%20save%20her%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ELet%20her%20go%3B%20abandon%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3EReturn%20now%20to%20your%20own%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EFor%20her%20punishment%20reaches%20to%20the%20heavens%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eit%20is%20so%20great%20it%20cannot%20be%20measured.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_exp